				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Canh-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-ni%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-x1HY9Hmqz-E6-xMz9JnWwA">Canh Tuất niên chế - 庚戌年製</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/D%E1%BA%A1-bi%E1%BB%87t-Vi-t%C6%B0-s%C4%A9/poem-LJwP9sdfybglH_VsulrdIQ">Dạ biệt Vi tư sĩ - 夜別韋司士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/author-daTT9TQ-QJ39piO86WPo5Q">Cao Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/D%E1%BB%AF-S%C6%A1n-Nam-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%87p-tr%E1%BA%A5n-quan-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%E1%BA%A7u-x%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-ho%E1%BA%A1-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-ADUUyqWYAkKSoljDcPCgHQ">Dữ Sơn Nam Thượng Hiệp trấn quan Trần Hầu xướng hoạ kỳ 5 - 與山南上協鎮官陳侯唱和其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ph%E1%BA%A3-L%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%A1n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Minh-t%E1%BB%B1-d%E1%BB%A5ng-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%B4ng-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qjl2wApzKYbvJoMDied55A">Đề Phả Lại sơn Đại Minh tự dụng thiếu bảo Trương công vận - 題普賴山大明寺用少保張公韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%89nh-h%E1%BB%93/poem-w30jYnld2Bjx-IVNJCeTTQ">Đỉnh hồ - 鼎湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/H%C6%B0u-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BA%A1p-h%E1%BB%A9ng-b%E1%BB%99-K%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-%C6%AFng-Tr%C3%ACnh-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-B%C3%ADnh-T%C3%BD-xu%C3%A2n-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-XLBAOQ1JJbUNOUBbP1DKnQ">Hưu đình tạp hứng, bộ Kính Đình Ưng Trình tiên sinh Bính Tý xuân cảm tác nguyên vận - 休亭雜興步敬亭膺脭先生丙子春感作原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-D%E1%BA%A7n/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BA%BF-ca/poem-1hV4jvJJuqid-9VQ_UAuiQ">Nhất thế ca - 一世歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-D%E1%BA%A7n/author-xraflgHOfFZLZePKI11Alg">Đường Dần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/T%E1%BA%A1-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-t%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-Kh%E1%BB%95ng-c%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-G2tpt59CWHsnu6SB1WllHA">Tạ Lưỡng Quảng tổng đốc Khổng công kỳ 1 - 謝兩廣總督孔公其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/author-Kf5yfK5iK_BR3H2g75GaXQ">Phạm Khiêm Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C3%A1t/Thi%C3%AAn-S%C6%A1n-ca/poem-MNQg-4L4zw2Dd1HbLOUHyA">Thiên Sơn ca - 天山歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C3%A1t/author-rT4JE0Ax7ttoqnPYUvKzPg">Hồng Lượng Cát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3EzsqreNmhqi-Xjv4vO76w">Vịnh sử kỳ 2 - 詠史其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
